Two scripts that I threw together to disable groups or re-enable groups in Office 365.

These scripts go along with my blog post about disabling Groups in Office 365 tenants:
https://wp.me/p37zvA-e8

To use the scripts, you'll have to have the Azure Active Directory Module for Windows PowerShell
installed. Instructions for this can be found in my blog post for remote PowerShell connections to
Office 365:
https://wp.me/p37zvA-b